attributes.description: This dashboard shows expanded user activity in Azure cloud.

query.esql:
FROM logs-*
| WHERE log.level == "Warning"
| WHERE user.name IS NOT NULL
| STATS `total` = COUNT() BY `time_bucket` = bucket(@timestamp, 50, ?_tstart, ?_tend)
| SORT `time_bucket` ASC

FROM logs-*
| WHERE log.level == "Warning"
| WHERE user.name IS NOT NULL

| SORT `time_bucket` ASC

FROM logs-*
| WHERE azure.operation.name LIKE "*LISTKEYS*"
| WHERE user.name IS NOT NULL
| STATS `success` = SUM(CASE(azure.result.type == "Success" OR azure.result.type == "Succeeded", 1, 0)), `fail` = SUM(CASE(azure.result.type == "Failed" OR azure.result.type == "Failure", 1, 0)) BY `time_bucket` = bucket(@timestamp, 50, ?_tstart, ?_tend)
| SORT `time_bucket` ASC

FROM logs-*

| STATS `total` = COUNT_DISTINCT(network.peer.address), `total_2` = COUNT() BY `email` = user.email, `name` = user.name

| WHERE `name` IS NOT NULL
| SORT `total_2` DESC
